The '''Yashaka Mountains''' were a range on planet [[Yashuvhu/Legends|Yashuvhu]].

They served as an isolated retreat where Force adept and former wanderer [[Valara Saar]], locally known as "Prophetess", placed her humble hut and trained some of her students.

